### Shelly Controller (internal Web API)
### Base URL is the Haus application server

@baseUrl = {{$dotenv HAUS_BASE_URL}}
@deviceId = YOUR_SHELLY_DEVICE_ID

### Get snapshots for all Shelly devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get readings (default limit 100)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly/readings
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get readings with custom limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly/readings?limit=50
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Get device status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly/status/{{deviceId}}
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Turn relay on
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly/relay/{{deviceId}}?on=true
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}

### Turn relay off
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/shelly/relay/{{deviceId}}?on=false
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv HAUS_API_AUTH}}
